{"tid":2024304,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"O記總警司疑僭建天台屋","createTime":"2020-05-19T13:55:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T16:01:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5a0b0ba03a66f424dffabac510008032b1ed646b","tid":2024304,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T13:55:57.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200519/O2RQHEFWHMPBKC5BOMPMMIDSDQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200519%2FO2RQHEFWHMPBKC5BOMPMMIDSDQ%2F&d=Vmg9VhgMmKCDk1oLDtgP7pugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=8ce468d6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200519%2FO2RQHEFWHMPBKC5BOMPMMIDSDQ%2F&h=114a9e5b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200519/O2RQHEFWHMPBKC5BOMPMMIDSDQ/</a><br />\n<br />\nO記總警司疑僭建天台屋<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】另一名涉嫌犯法的警隊高層為有組織罪案及三合會調查科（O記）總警司黃維，其居住大埔錦麗園的單位，天台疑有僭建物。土地註冊資料顯示，黃維1995年購入錦麗園單位，天台屋則在2016至2017年期間加設，意味天台的懷疑僭建物存在至少達三年半。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nO記總警司黃維（圓圖）的大埔錦麗園單位疑僭建天台屋及改建圍欄。<br />\n拆石屎圍欄 違規逾三年<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：新界北副指揮官五物業霸官地僭建  接地政警告六年拒還原<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據土地註冊紀錄，<br />\n.....................................<br />\n對外的窗戶均用錫紙覆蓋，私隱度十足。<br />\n<br />\n本報翻查該處的Google Earth高空圖，<br />\n.................................<br />\n意味天台屋僭建物存在至少達三年半。<br />\n<br />\n根據錦麗園地契附載，<br />\n....................................<br />\n部份天台亦如黃般搭建天台屋。<br />\n<br />\n去年6月21日，灣仔警察總部被市民圍堵，<br />\n...............................<br />\n當日疑遇襲致手骹紅腫受傷，曾送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示不評論個別個案，<br />\n..................................<br />\n我唔知鄧炳強仲會唔會話好神聖？我真係唔知點神聖？唔通僭建越多就越神聖？」<br />\n<br />\n本報調查組"},{"pid":"800286814b0b7cf38b9c7fa406d033c7d3575abc","tid":2024304,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T14:10:59.000Z","msg":"想侵犯神？立心不祥？"},{"pid":"a4f718bbaa3aa469571e6f2dc30416e0e4ac5096","tid":2024304,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T14:59:41.000Z","msg":"不如淨係報D無僭建既出黎啦<br />\n根本個個都污糟邋遢 逐個報都嘥氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ed65792968bc1627d1f1eb0c8bd94447022dea2","tid":2024304,"uid":2924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T15:50:11.000Z","msg":"全港最大僭建集團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62c2952da6521d486a8d713ed9eaabd496b42add","tid":2024304,"uid":116981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T16:01:39.000Z","msg":"試下咁講<br />\n<br />\n警隊成為犯罪天堂，罪犯只要係警員，犯罪就可以冇事，咁會破壞香港既國際地位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}